<p><b>Father's Day</b> is a day honoring <a href="/wiki/Father" title="Father">fathers</a>, celebrated on various days in many places around the world. It complements <a href="/wiki/Mother%27s_Day" title="Mother's Day">Mother's Day</a>, the celebration honoring <a href="/wiki/Mother" title="Mother">mothers</a>.</p>
